summary: AN ORDINANCE repealing Sections 64, 65, 65-A, 66, 67 and 68 of the License Code (Ordinance 48022) which provide for the licensing and regulation of public card rooms, and amending Sections 5-A, 11, 11-A, and 19 of the License Code and Section 3 of Ordinance 75088 to delete references to public card rooms and public card room licenses.
